1) Space + Space -> Fly
2) Shift -> x2 Speed
3) M -> Open Hacks Menu
4) N -> Noclip (It only works if you have entered the other player's base at least once, If the player leaves and a new one enters, the procedure must be repeated)
5) Auto Close Base
6) Q -> Set Teleport Point
7) Z -> Teleport To The Indicated Point
